    <item>
      <title>印度航空乘客因纽约炸弹威胁而延误</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-19/air-india-passengers-delayed-by-hoax-bomb-threat-in-new-york</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周六，印度航空从孟买抵达纽约的乘客因收到虚假炸弹威胁而延误，这是该航空公司本月收到的一系列虚假警报中的又一例。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-19/air-india-passengers-delayed-by-hoax-bomb-threat-in-new-york</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 19 Oct 2024 18:11:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西监管机构指控美洲前首席执行官进行内幕交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-19/brazil-regulator-accuses-ex-americanas-ceo-of-insider-trading</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西证券监管机构指控美洲百货公司前首席执行官米格尔·古铁雷斯 (Miguel Gutierrez) 和其他 7 人从事内幕交易，指控他们在该零售巨头重大会计丑闻披露之前不当使用特权信息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-19/brazil-regulator-accuses-ex-americanas-ceo-of-insider-trading</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 19 Oct 2024 17:40:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>TGI Friday’s 寻求新融资，为破产做准备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-19/tgi-friday-s-seeks-new-financing-in-preparation-for-bankruptcy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，休闲餐饮连锁店 TGI Friday’s Inc. 正寻求融资，准备在未来几周申请破产保护。此前，迫于顾客预算紧缩和对快餐的偏好，该公司难以扭转业务局面。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-19/tgi-friday-s-seeks-new-financing-in-preparation-for-bankruptcy</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 19 Oct 2024 16:10:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度经济繁荣将推动私人信贷和债券扩张</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-19/india-boom-set-to-drive-private-credit-and-bond-expansion-credit-weekly</link>
      <description><![CDATA[现在与国际金融界的任何人交谈，讨论迟早都会转向印度。该国债券正被纳入全球指数，吸引了一些押注强劲经济增长的市场最大基金经理。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-19/india-boom-set-to-drive-private-credit-and-bond-expansion-credit-weekly</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 19 Oct 2024 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比特币矿工在收益“减半”六个月后走上了不同的道路</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-19/bitcoin-miners-pivoting-to-ai-outperform-hodlers-six-months-after-halving</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在比特币网络验证交易的奖励减少了一半六个月后，加密货币挖矿公司正在选择两条不同的道路来维持生存。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-19/bitcoin-miners-pivoting-to-ai-outperform-hodlers-six-months-after-halving</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 19 Oct 2024 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>宝马因火灾隐患在华召回近 70 万辆汽车</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-18/bmw-recalls-almost-700-000-cars-in-china-on-fire-safety-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[宝马汽车公司 (BMW AG) 因冷却泵缺陷在中国召回近 70 万辆汽车，这对于已深陷其他车辆故障泥潭的德国汽车制造商而言，无疑是雪上加霜。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-18/bmw-recalls-almost-700-000-cars-in-china-on-fire-safety-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 18 Oct 2024 14:50:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
